<codeline lineno="1"><highlight class="comment">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="2"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@file<sp/>event_template.dox</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Detailed<sp/>documentation<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>EventTemplate<sp/>Cython<sp/>class.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@page<sp/>EventTemplate_page<sp/>EventTemplate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventTemplate_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>Cython-implemented<sp/>class<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework,<sp/>serving<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>foundational<sp/>template<sp/>for<sp/>event-based<sp/>data<sp/>structures.<sp/>It<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>event<sp/>object,<sp/>enabling<sp/>efficient<sp/>data<sp/>manipulation<sp/>and<sp/>access<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>environment.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>inherited<sp/>by<sp/>more<sp/>specific<sp/>event<sp/>implementations,<sp/>providing<sp/>common<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>event<sp/>indexing,<sp/>weighting,<sp/>and<sp/>tree/branch<sp/>management.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventTemplate_class<sp/>The<sp/>EventTemplate<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>it&apos;s<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type,<sp/>allowing<sp/>direct<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>C++<sp/>objects<sp/>and<sp/>types<sp/>for<sp/>performance<sp/>optimization.<sp/>It<sp/>encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>object,<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>and<sp/>exposing<sp/>its<sp/>properties<sp/>and<sp/>methods<sp/>to<sp/>Python.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>EventTemplate_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent.<sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>called<sp/>when<sp/>the<sp/>object<sp/>is<sp/>allocated.<sp/>If<sp/>the<sp/>instance<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>itself<sp/>(i.e.,<sp/>it&apos;s<sp/>a<sp/>subclass),<sp/>it<sp/>returns<sp/>immediately.<sp/>Otherwise,<sp/>it<sp/>allocates<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer.<sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty,<sp/>as<sp/>initialization<sp/>logic<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent.<sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>called<sp/>when<sp/>the<sp/>object<sp/>is<sp/>deallocated.<sp/>If<sp/>the<sp/>instance<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>itself,<sp/>it<sp/>returns.<sp/>Otherwise,<sp/>it<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.ptr`,<sp/>preventing<sp/>memory<sp/>leaks.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>EventTemplate_special_methods<sp/>Special<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__name__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Returns<sp/>the<sp/>name<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>event<sp/>object<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>string.<sp/>It<sp/>uses<sp/>the<sp/>`env`<sp/>utility<sp/>function<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>string<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>string.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__hash__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Computes<sp/>a<sp/>hash<sp/>value<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>event.<sp/>It<sp/>converts<sp/>the<sp/>first<sp/>8<sp/>characters<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>object&apos;s<sp/>hash<sp/>string<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>integer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__eq__(self,<sp/>other)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Compares<sp/>two<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>objects<sp/>for<sp/>equality.<sp/>It<sp/>first<sp/>checks<sp/>if<sp/>`other`<sp/>is<sp/>an<sp/>instance<sp/>or<sp/>subclass<sp/>of<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>using<sp/>`is_self`.<sp/>If<sp/>so,<sp/>it<sp/>compares<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>`event_template`<sp/>objects.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`is_self(self,<sp/>inpt)<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>bool`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>A<sp/>utility<sp/>method<sp/>to<sp/>check<sp/>if<sp/>the<sp/>given<sp/>input<sp/>`inpt`<sp/>is<sp/>an<sp/>instance<sp/>of<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>subclass<sp/>thereof.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="36"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>EventTemplate_properties<sp/>Properties</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>following<sp/>properties<sp/>provide<sp/>controlled<sp/>access<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>`event_template`&apos;s<sp/>data<sp/>members.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>index<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>int`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="40"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>the<sp/>integer<sp/>index<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="41"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@index.setter<sp/>index(self,<sp/>val:<sp/>Union[str,<sp/>double])`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="42"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>index<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event.<sp/>It<sp/>attempts<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`index`<sp/>directly.<sp/>If<sp/>a<sp/>`TypeError`<sp/>occurs<sp/>(e.g.,<sp/>`val`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>string),<sp/>it<sp/>assumes<sp/>`val`<sp/>represents<sp/>a<sp/>leaf<sp/>name<sp/>and<sp/>stores<sp/>it<sp/>in<sp/>`self.ptr.leaves`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="43"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="44"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>weight<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>double`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="45"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>the<sp/>double-precision<sp/>floating-point<sp/>weight<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="46"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@weight.setter<sp/>weight(self,<sp/>val:<sp/>Union[str,<sp/>double])`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="47"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>weight<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>event.<sp/>Similar<sp/>to<sp/>`index.setter`,<sp/>it<sp/>handles<sp/>`TypeError`<sp/>by<sp/>storing<sp/>`val`<sp/>in<sp/>`self.ptr.leaves`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="49"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>Tree<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>str`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="50"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>the<sp/>name<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>primary<sp/>ROOT<sp/>tree<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="51"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@Tree.setter<sp/>Tree(self,<sp/>str<sp/>val)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="52"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>name<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>primary<sp/>ROOT<sp/>tree.<sp/>It<sp/>uses<sp/>the<sp/>`enc`<sp/>utility<sp/>function<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>string<sp/>`val`<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>string.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="53"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="54"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>Trees<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>list`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="55"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>a<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>all<sp/>ROOT<sp/>tree<sp/>names<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="56"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@Trees.setter<sp/>Trees(self,<sp/>val:<sp/>Union[str,<sp/>list])`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="57"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>ROOT<sp/>tree<sp/>names.<sp/>It<sp/>can<sp/>accept<sp/>a<sp/>single<sp/>string<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>strings.<sp/>If<sp/>a<sp/>list,<sp/>it<sp/>iterates<sp/>and<sp/>calls<sp/>the<sp/>setter<sp/>for<sp/>each<sp/>element.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="58"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="59"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>Branches<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>list`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="60"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>a<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>all<sp/>ROOT<sp/>branch<sp/>names<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="61"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@Branches.setter<sp/>Branches(self,<sp/>val:<sp/>Union[str,<sp/>list])`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="62"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>ROOT<sp/>branch<sp/>names.<sp/>Similar<sp/>to<sp/>`Trees.setter`,<sp/>it<sp/>handles<sp/>single<sp/>strings<sp/>or<sp/>lists<sp/>of<sp/>strings.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="63"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="64"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>Name`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="65"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>the<sp/>name<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>event<sp/>object.<sp/>This<sp/>appears<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>a<sp/>duplicate<sp/>of<sp/>`__name__`<sp/>but<sp/>exposed<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>property.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="66"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="67"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>EventTemplate_cpp_interaction<sp/>C++<sp/>Interaction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="68"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>class<sp/>heavily<sp/>relies<sp/>on<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>ability<sp/>to<sp/>interact<sp/>with<sp/>C++.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="69"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>EventTemplate`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
