<codeline lineno="74"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`env(self.ptr.name)`<sp/>and<sp/>`enc(val)`:<sp/>These<sp/>functions<sp/>(presumably<sp/>from<sp/>`AnalysisG.core.tools`)<sp/>handle<sp/>the<sp/>conversion<sp/>between<sp/>C++<sp/>`std::string`<sp/>and<sp/>Python<sp/>`str`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="75"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
